A 1D harmonic oscillator of mass $m$ and frequency $omega$ is described by ladder operators $a, a^dagger$. What is the commutator $[a, (a^dagger)^n]$?
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$n (a^dagger)^(n-1)$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$1$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$n a^dagger$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$0$
